Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.420 --> 00:00:03.140
Ko‘pgina telefonlarda sayohat paytida 
qo‘l keladigan joriy valyutani 

00:00:03.140 --> 00:00:04.480
konvertatsiyalash ilovalari mavjud.

00:00:04.480 --> 00:00:06.850
Ushbu mashq mana bu misol bilan bog‘liq.

00:00:06.850 --> 00:00:10.500
Bunda biz AQSh dollarini 
Yapon Yenasiga o‘zgartirmoqchimiz.

00:00:10.500 --> 00:00:13.330
Joriy kurs 1 AQSh dollariga 
119 yapon yenasiga teng.

00:00:13.330 --> 00:00:17.240
Deylik, biz 40 dollarni konvertatsiya qilamiz.

00:00:17.240 --> 00:00:18.700
Keling, u biz kutgan narsaga mos 
keladimi yoki yo‘qligini ko‘rish 

00:00:18.700 --> 00:00:19.450
uchun qo‘l simulyatsiyasini qilaylik.

00:00:19.450 --> 00:00:23.110
Birinchi satrda biz dollars deb 
nomlangan o‘zgaruvchini e’lon qilamiz 

00:00:23.110 --> 00:00:24.720
va qiymatni 40 ga o‘rnatib boshlaymiz.

00:00:24.720 --> 00:00:28.540
Ushbu o‘zgaruvchi biz o‘zgartirmoqchi 
bo‘lgan miqdorimizni saqlayotgan bo‘lsa kerak.

00:00:28.540 --> 00:00:29.294
Yaxshi.

00:00:29.294 --> 00:00:31.680
Keyingi qatorda bizda dollarsToYen 
deb nomlangan o‘zgaruvchi bor.

00:00:31.680 --> 00:00:33.930
Va biz buning qiymatini 119 deb beramiz.

00:00:33.930 --> 00:00:37.250
Ushbu o‘zgaruvchi konvertatsiya 
stavkasini ifodalaydi, 

00:00:37.250 --> 00:00:39.100
ya’ni 1 dollar 119 yenaga teng.

00:00:39.100 --> 00:00:42.220
Keyin biz yen deb nomlangan o‘zgaruvchini 
e’lon qilamiz va ishga tushiramiz.

00:00:42.220 --> 00:00:45.110
Endi biz boshlang‘ich qiymatini beramiz.

00:00:45.110 --> 00:00:48.620
Shunday qilib, bu yerda bizda 119 ga 
teng dollarsToYen o‘zgaruvchisi bor.

00:00:48.620 --> 00:00:51.050
Va biz uni 40 ga teng bo‘lgan 
dollars ga ko‘paytirmoqdamiz.

00:00:51.050 --> 00:00:53.150
Men buning uchun kalkulyatordan foydalandim.

00:00:53.150 --> 00:00:55.554
Natija bu yerda 4,760.

00:00:55.554 --> 00:00:59.780
Keyingi qatorda biz 4,760 ni ekranga chiqaramiz.

00:00:59.780 --> 00:01:01.640
Xo‘sh, bu ishni to‘g‘ri qildimi?

00:01:01.640 --> 00:01:04.360
Bilamizki, 1 dollar 119 yenga teng va 
agar bizda 2 dollar bo‘lsa, 

00:01:04.360 --> 00:01:08.570
1 dollardan ko‘ra ikki baravar ko‘p bo‘ladi.

00:01:08.570 --> 00:01:15.240
Bu 119 ni ikkiga ko‘paytirganga teng va agar bizda 40 dollar bo‘lsa, bu 40 karra 119 ga teng bo‘ladi.

00:01:15.240 --> 00:01:17.370
Bu yerda biz aniq hisob-kitob qildik.

00:01:17.370 --> 00:01:20.470
Xo‘sh, ha, bu yen miqdorini 
to‘g‘ri hisoblab chiqmoqda.

